##### Description
* Social Media, mailing lists are all potential targets for investigation
* Simply formulate an appropriate question, or even small survey
* Make sure it tests one or more actual hypotheses

##### Tips
* Be very aware of the culture and rules of conduct that apply
  * Is it ok to post an open call for feedback?
  * Is it ok to post a questionnaire?
* As usual, tie your questions to one or more hypothesis
* Understand the audience who will see your message. Is it the one you want?
